column1: This campaign has never been about Don Young – it has always been about who can get the job done and fight for Alaska. I'm looking forward to continuing my service on behalf of our great state in the 117th Congress.

Our campaign is extremely pleased and grateful for the support we have received. We told the truth and worked hard to earn every vote. Right now we feel very good about the election and want to thank the thousands of Alaskans across the state for their continued support! https://t.co/7tb8Db8O0b
